Christopher Zacharie

Owner/Director, Creative Excellence Tutoring Center
He/Him/His Houston, Tx

With 12 years of experience as a dedicated 3rd grade teacher in the League City area and 2 years as an HIV Prevention Specialist at the Galveston County Health District, I have developed a strong foundation in education and public health. I've also leveraged my skills and expertise as an E-commerce Entrepreneur, managing two online shopsone specializing in print-on-demand products, and the other offering a wide range of quality and affordable products. Now, Im returning to my passion for education in a new way by launching my own tutoring business, where I will provide exceptional, personalized tutoring that fosters academic excellence and creative growth. My goal is to empower students to become confident, innovative thinkers who can positively impact their communities and the world.
